column4: Re: Adry Fashion x For Bloggers Only
column6:
Hi guys, 
 Just thought I'd quickly touch base again to see whether you're open to having a chat about working with our influencers?  
 We've helped many fashion and beauty brands increase their sales and social media numbers with our stunning campaigns. Happy to send through our Media Kit for you with some examples. 
 If you're not the right person to contact in relation to this, please let me know. 
 Chat soon, Liza 
 Liza Chavez Collaborations Manager 
 W: www.forbloggersonly.com        Instagram // Facebook 
 

 
 From: Liza Chavez <liza@forbloggersonly.com>
Date: 2018-12-03 14:57:40.709
To: "support@innovfashion.com" <support@innovfashion.com>
Subject: Adry Fashion x For Bloggers Only

 Hi Guys, 
 We are a boutique platform that connects top-tier influencers, with like-minded brands, and unlike other influencer platforms, we believe in "Quality over Quantity." 
 Our Influencers absolutely love Adry Fashion and we've been receiving requests to make your pieces available to them. You can see our team HERE. 
 Our collaborations are entirely organic, meaning that our brands work on a gifting basis, rather than a sponsored one. 
 If you'd love to see your brand on the world's best influencers, let's have a chat about how we can collaborate. 
 If you'd like to unsubscribe or aren't the right person to reach out to, please let me know. 
 Thanks in advance, Liza 
 Liza Chavez Collaborations Manager 
 W: www.forbloggersonly.com        Instagram // Facebook

Hi,
One of your customers may have used us (Trackingmore : all-in-one global package tracking tool. Support track and trace international 561 couriers. API docs, delivery notification and parcel tracking plugins are available) to track her package. So she sent an email to us possibly because of mistaking us as a seller.  It seems she is not satisfied with the email you guys replied ( which is an auto one I guess).  Maybe we can help you out of this problem. More than 500 couriers are trackable here and auto-notification to customers may better customers' shopping experience. More in-time parcel info, fewer worries or refunds. Just a suggestion, hope it helps. 

Best,
Vanessa
Skype: vanessa_7134
Website: www.trackingmore.com

Hi,
Sorry about that. Trackingmore is a free shipment tracking platform instead of a courier company or a merchant. If you want to track your packages, you can choose the corresponding courier, enter the tracking number and click "Track". Then the tracking information you need will be shown at once. https://www.trackingmore.com/carriers.html
If you want to get a refund, highly recommend you to contact the merchant directly. And I'll help you to send an email to notify them, too. Here is the shipping and returns policy of the online shop you purchased from. Hope it helps. There is gonna be a way to work it out. 

Best regards,
Vanessa
